Pros: - Open extension - add new storage types without changing wrapper - Template parameter hiding - LazyViewStorage&lt;ViewType&gt; can be stored without exposing ViewType - Familiar OOP pattern
Cons: - Virtual call overhead per access - Heap allocation for storage instance



